---
title: Goat Cheese, Walnut and Honey Crostini with Fennel and Strawberry-Rhubarb Salad
description: Rhubarb is typically used in desserts, but in this recipe, we're pickling it and turning it into an amazing dressing for salad! It pairs delightfully with goat cheese crostini.
